SELECT r.route_id, r.source_location, r.destination_location, ro.optimization_details FROM routes r JOIN route_optimization ro ON r.route_id = ro.route_id WHERE ro.optimization_status = 'completed' ORDER BY r.route_id ASC LIMIT 5;

SELECT r.route_id, r.source_location, r.destination_location, ro.optimization_status FROM routes r LEFT JOIN route_optimization ro ON r.route_id = ro.route_id WHERE ro.optimization_status IS NULL ORDER BY r.route_id ASC LIMIT 5;
